# webPlugInInitialize()

**Instance Method**

Initializes the plug-in.

## Declaration

```swift
func webPlugInInitialize()
```

## Discussion

Tells the plug-in to perform one-time initialization. This method must be called only once per instance of the plug-in object, before any other methods in the protocol are called.

## Controlling the Plug-in

- **webPlugInDestroy()**: Prepares the plug-in for deallocation.
- **webPlugInStart()**: Tells the plug-in to start normal operation.
- **webPlugInStop()**: Tells the plug-in to stop normal operation.
